Package <Unnamed>

Interface Summary
ThreadListener ThreadListener defines a class that can have a threader run it
 

Class Summary
Node The node class defines a Node to be used in a linked list, which has a reference to a Particle, the previous Node, and the next Node
Octant Octant class defines a cube which has dimensions and a list of particles contained within it
Octree The Octree class defines a three dimensional binary tree.
Particle The Particle class defines a particle, with a mass, a location, a speed, a net force, and a color.
Particle3D The Particle3D class defines a particle in 3 dimensional space with a mass, a location, a speed, a net force, and a color.
ParticleSystem The Particle System class defines a system of particles.
ParticleSystem3D The Particle System class defines a system of particles.
Quadrant Quadrant class defines a square field which has dimensions and a list of particles contained within it
Quadtree The Quadtree class defines a two dimensional binary tree.
Simulation The Simulation class is the Applet.
Threader The Threader class defines the thread that runs the physics of the simulation
TreeNode TreeNode class defines a Node in a quadtree
TreeNode3D TreeNode3D class defines a Node in an octree
Universe The Universe class is the main worker of the program.
